//   3. Realtime<Crit> composition with `frame_clock_end_and_pace` for
//      the audio-callback frame-pacing pattern (per
//      examples/audio_callback.cssl). Stage-0 the composition is
//      documented but not type-checked.
//   4. KAN-bias hooks for per-display + per-scene learning of the
//      dyn-res lerp curve (T11-W18+ deferred · per Apocky-spec).
//   5. Loop-form migration (manual tail-recursion → flat `while`/`loop`)
//      once the parser recognizes those at all stmt-positions.
//   6. f32 / fixed-point helper migration : the Rust reference exposes
//      `scale_f32()` for telemetry/HUD ; CSSL parser does not yet
//      type-check f32 ↔ u32 conversions in const positions, deferred.
